    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968370/extras/88b5f2e29affbadd7557259b21b48ee5.poster.avif?t=1750428330\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968370/extras/88b5f2e29affbadd7557259b21b48ee5.webm?t=1750428330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968370/extras/88b5f2e29affbadd7557259b21b48ee5.mp4?t=1750428330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>驱魔使徒</strong> 是一款点击冒险解谜游戏，你将扮演使徒巴塞洛缪斯，他的神圣使命就是解放腐败的罗特博克城，勇敢面对潜伏在城中的邪恶，揭开迷雾笼罩的真相，将代表七大罪的恶魔们赶尽杀绝。<br><br>巴塞洛缪斯在2000年的岁月里反复往返人间驱逐恶魔，看似已经是家常便饭了。但是，这一次的事情似乎并不那么简单，似乎有某个“存在”插手进来......<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968370/extras/89b393b26440693b6db6aa9b01074d2b.poster.avif?t=1750428330\" width=580 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968370/extras/89b393b26440693b6db6aa9b01074d2b.webm?t=1750428330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968370/extras/89b393b26440693b6db6aa9b01074d2b.mp4?t=1750428330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏灵感来自于《银翼杀手》、《断剑》系列或《狩魔猎人》等游戏，<strong>驱魔使徒</strong>以强大的故事情节、流畅感和黑暗氛围为基础。<br><br>用你的聪明才智去解决各种陷阱和谜题，猎杀恶魔，摧毁他们的野心。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968370/extras/4ff6b33832e624812e0575747acdaa04.poster.avif?t=1750428330\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968370/extras/4ff6b33832e624812e0575747acdaa04.webm?t=1750428330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>自由探索由99个手绘场景组成的魔幻世界，海量微小的细节等着你发现。<br></li><li>沉浸式叙事情节，沉重却不缺乏搞笑!<br></li><li>独特的漫画分镜风格体验剧情！<br></li><li>各种谜题，挑战和迷你游戏，带给玩家多种多样的游戏乐趣。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968370/extras/d44fdd8f00b8694011684a39888369c8.avif?t=1750428330\" width=580 height=354 /></span><br><br><strong>驱魔使徒</strong> 不仅仅采用了知名的点击游戏模式，同时还在基础上创新了更多新鲜的要素，给你带来一段不同的旅程。<br><br>如果你喜欢剧情游戏，并想体验一个包含深意与反思的动漫故事，你也许会喜欢我们的游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968370/extras/a7d464099c2a8737ab46662e8ed8c675.avif?t=1750428330\" width=580 height=894 /></span>",
